enchantment.minecraft.fire_aspect.desc.r: Ignites attacked mobs. Usable as Flint and Steel when sneaking.
enchantment.minecraft.channeling.desc.re: Causes the Trident to summon lightning when striking a mob while it's thundering. Ignites attacked mobs.

enchantment.minecraft.luck_of_the_sea.de: Increases the quality of fishing loot and decreases the time required for fish to bite.
advancements.adventure.two_birds_one_arr: Kill two Phantoms with one crossbow shot
enchantment.minecraft.protection.desc: Decreases damage taken from all sources.
enchantment.minecraft.fire_protection.de: Greatly decreases damage taken from and time spent on fire.
enchantment.minecraft.feather_falling.de: Greatly decreases damage taken from falling.
enchantment.minecraft.blast_protection.d: Greatly decreases damage taken from explosions.
enchantment.minecraft.projectile_protect: Greatly decreases damage taken from projectiles.
enchantment.minecraft.thorns.desc: Harms attackers when you take damage.
enchantment.minecraft.binding_curse.desc: Prevents you from unequipping the item.
enchantment.minecraft.soul_speed.desc: Increases movement speed on soul blocks.
enchantment.minecraft.smite.desc: Greatly increases damage dealt to undead.
enchantment.minecraft.bane_of_arthropods: Greatly increases damage dealt to and slows arthropods.
enchantment.minecraft.sweeping.desc: Increases damage dealt with sweeping attacks.
enchantment.minecraft.silk_touch.desc: Causes certain blocks to drop themselves.
enchantment.minecraft.infinity.desc: Causes normal arrows to not be consumed.
enchantment.minecraft.luck_of_the_sea.de: Increases the quality of fishing loot.
enchantment.minecraft.lure.desc: Decreases the time required for fish to bite.
enchantment.minecraft.loyalty.desc: Causes the Trident to return to you upon landing.
enchantment.minecraft.impaling.desc: Greatly increases damage dealt to aquatic mobs.
enchantment.minecraft.riptide.desc: Allows you to launch yourself with the Trident when wet.
enchantment.minecraft.channeling.desc: Causes the Trident to summon lightning when striking a mob while it's thundering.
enchantment.minecraft.multishot.desc: Causes three arrows to shoot instead of one.
enchantment.minecraft.piercing.desc: Causes projectiles to pierce through mobs and shields.
enchantment.minecraft.mending.desc: Causes experience orbs to repair the item.
enchantment.minecraft.vanishing_curse.de: Causes the item to disappear on death.
enchantment.enchancement.assimilation.de: Automatically consumes food when you're hungry, prioritizing off hand. Food and drinks are consumed faster.
enchantment.enchancement.perception.desc: Increases visibilty in the dark and causes mobs to be seen through walls.
enchantment.enchancement.veil.desc: Decreases monster detection range and hides your name behind walls.
enchantment.enchancement.amphibious.desc: Increases underwater mining and movement speed. Decreases air consumption underwater and time spent on fire.
enchantment.enchancement.strafe.desc: Increases air mobility. Double tapping [%s] launches you in your movement direction.
enchantment.enchancement.wardenspine.des: Harms attackers and greatly decreases damage taken from behind.
enchantment.enchancement.dash.desc: Sneaking in the air launches you in your look direction.
enchantment.enchancement.slide.desc: Holding your sprint key causes you to slide constantly. Sneaking in the air causes you to slam towards the ground, knocking back mobs and negating fall damage.
enchantment.enchancement.buoy.desc: Causes you to walk on fluids, descending via sneaking. Holding jump while submerged rapidly propels you upwards. Prevents floating.
enchantment.enchancement.bouncy.desc: Negates fall damage. Launches you upwards upon landing while not sneaking. Sneaking while grounded will charge a super jump.
enchantment.enchancement.gale.desc: Allows you to jump two more times in the air.
enchantment.enchancement.berserk.desc: Increases damage dealt proportional to missing health.
enchantment.enchancement.frostbite.desc: Freezes attacked mobs. When killed, turns them into ice statues that can be moved or shattered, launching ice shards that freeze other mobs.
enchantment.enchancement.chaos.desc: Gives normal arrows a random negative potion effect, or positive if sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.delay.desc: Arrows will not launch immediately after shooting, building up damage over time. Can be launched prematurely by punching, and additionally redirected by sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.phasing.desc: Causes arrows to have no gravity and phase through blocks, upon which they regain gravity.
enchantment.enchancement.brimstone.desc: Fires a piercing laser that ignores armor and increases damage with charge and distance. Costs health to fire.
enchantment.enchancement.scatter.desc: Allows Amethyst Shards to be loaded which explode into a burst of projectiles.
enchantment.enchancement.torch.desc: Allows rapid loading of Torches that ignite shot mobs. Torches that land on a block will be placed if fired while sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.leech.desc: Regenerates health when dealing damage. Thrown Tridents will temporarily stick to mobs and deal damage.
enchantment.enchancement.warp.desc: Teleports you to the location of the Trident if it didn't hit a mob.
enchantment.enchancement.extracting.desc: Extracts materials from connected ores, leaving the stone behind. Disabled while sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.molten.desc: Smelts mined blocks. Disabled while sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.beheading.desc: Slain mobs and players have a chance to drop their head.
enchantment.enchancement.lumberjack.desc: Connected logs will also be destroyed. Disabled while sneaking.
enchantment.enchancement.bury.desc: Using on a mob will bury it if the ground below is soft enough.
enchantment.enchancement.scooping.desc: Deals extra damage and increases mob loot drops.
enchantment.enchancement.disarm.desc: Steals or disables a latched entity's held item.
enchantment.enchancement.grapple.desc: Allows the Fishing Bobber to latch onto blocks. Launches you towards that block upon release. Reels in entities with more strength.
